race.comment: FLY WITH CAUTION (12) just missed over this course and distance last start when bumping into a good one 35 days ago. Comes into this on the fresh side, but he tends to do his best work that way and he still has plenty of upside. Steve Parnham rides now and he can go one better in the feature. REDBACK FLYER (13) gritted his teeth to fend off his rivals over the mile last time out and looks better suited getting out in trip today. He'll need some luck from the outside barrier, but he drops in weight and does possess some tactical speed. Continues to build and can repeat the dose. FAMOUS DAIN (11) jumped the $1.85 favourite in the Ascot Mile last time out when a touch disappointing when sitting on the speed. Out in trip again now is the query, but he brings in some strong form and he's not out of this from a good draw. SILVER EYE (6) has to be included as he eyes off the hat-trick. ROCKING SOCIETY (7) resumes here off a good effort in the Perth Cup and is worth thought.
